Glad to see we're getting some seeders. I know it's a big torrent, but what do you expect for straight dvd rips? WITH DELETED SCENES EVEN! I hope everyone enjoys these as much as I did and shows their appreciation by seeding!

By the way, deleted scenes and such are on disc 3


@MrSketchtastic: Nobody said anything about Seasons, as oversoul53 explained, FamilyGuy releases their dvds through volumes that include the second half of one season and the first half of the next. So yes, this torrent is exactly as advertised.

@TheEnlightened: If you're able to get to the vob files, then that means you're able to mount the iso, which means you can just open the disc in any media player, as I said I use VLC, I also have HP QuickPlay on my laptop which works quite well. I find it less confusing to just run the whole disc. That way, you get the dvd menus.
